Protecting YOUR Privacy
It is TRAN QUANG LONG principle to respect the privacy of the personal information of our users .
TRAN QUANG LONG will take reasonable measures to protect user’s personal information, without 
disclosing such information to any third party other than its Partners (without the consent of 
the user), unless such disclosure is (i) required by law, court order or competent government 
departments or (ii) agreed to by the user. Exceptions will be applied if the user selects to accept
such disclosures during the registration process (where applicable), or is otherwise stipulated on
the disclosure or use of a user’s personal information between the user and TRAN QUANG LONG  STUDIO
and its Partners. The user shall bear any risks that may arise from any authorized disclosure of a
user’s personal information. For the operation and improvement of LONG GCD STUDIO’s technologies 
and applications, TRAN QUANG LONG  STUDIO may collect and use the non-personal information of its 
users, or provide such information to third parties, in order to provide better user experience and
improve the quality of our applications.Permission we use
